{"tid":2278894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搜尋「loser」，Twitter即彈出特朗普；搜尋「winner」，Twitter指向拜登賬戶","createTime":"2020-11-09T12:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T12:14:05.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"966f73439953635bce47009d456dff3c100a01f3","tid":2278894,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n拜登前日獲得美國主流傳媒確認勝選，總統特朗普則拒絕認輸。究竟孰贏孰輸，原來Twitter早有定論。<br />\n<br />\n搜「贏家」指向拜登賬戶<br />\n在傳媒前日早上宣告拜登勝利的幾乎同時，路透社發現在Twitter以「loser」（輸家）一字搜尋「人物」（People），得出的結果第一項就是特朗普的賬戶；以「winner」（贏家）兩個單字搜索，則會被指向拜登與副手賀錦麗的賬戶。<br />\nTwitter聲稱，搜尋結果是基於平台用戶在推文中如何使用有關字眼而自動產生。「假如某一賬戶經常被用戶與某些字眼相提並論，在演算上就會被聯繫起來。」Twitter在聲明中強調：「這種關聯只是暫時性，會隨着人們推文趨勢而不斷改變。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/UXMQLM2F2RE7TACXIYVNS2WMLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FUXMQLM2F2RE7TACXIYVNS2WMLY%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=2ec98173\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FUXMQLM2F2RE7TACXIYVNS2WMLY%2F&h=abee077e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/UXMQLM2F2RE7TACXIYVNS2WMLY/</a>"},{"pid":"91c2b2416b769d317c96d3a2e026d1c0c20c1ed6","tid":2278894,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好肉酸"},{"pid":"9d190b30615e3f60cf6411eaa603636b3f852d69","tid":2278894,"uid":57073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"左派真係好核突"},{"pid":"7efe9cc01e0760375987890e577457a33f254b8d","tid":2278894,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:12:23.000Z","msg":"Twitter 同垃圾場已經冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f4bd75b22580af926906cde1fbd4d111ecbbc5","tid":2278894,"uid":12075